Kachenjunga Conservation Area, near Ghunsa village. Summit: GLORIA sites NP-KCJ-SMD. Collectors: Ghimire, S.K.; Salick, Jan; Konchar, Katie.

Tampe-la. Wangchuck Centennial Park. On way to GLORIA sites BT-TPL. Collaborative collection done by National Biodiversity Centre (NBC) and MO. Collectors included: Suresh K. Ghimire, Robbie Hart, Choki Gyeltshen, Natalie Konig, Kezang Tobgay, Kencho Dorji, Rinchen Dorji, Nima Gyeltshen, Tsering Pem & Nidup Gyeltshen.

Jomolhari. GLORIA site located within the Jigme Dorji Wangchuck National Park. GLORIA site BT-JML, outside of summits. Collaborative collection done by National Biodiversity Centre (NBC) and MO. Collectors: Sangay Dema, Suresh K. Ghimire, & Robbie Hart.
